flowchart TD
    D[Deploy Canary] --> W1[1% Traffic]
    W1 --> E1{Metrics OK?}
    E1 -->|Yes| W2[5% Traffic]
    E1 -->|No| RB[Rollback]
    W2 --> E2{Metrics OK?}
    E2 -->|Yes| W3[25% Traffic]
    E2 -->|No| RB
    W3 --> E3{Metrics OK?}
    E3 -->|Yes| W4[50% Traffic]
    E3 -->|No| RB
    W4 --> E4{Metrics OK?}
    E4 -->|Yes| FULL[100% Traffic]
    E4 -->|No| RB
    FULL --> DONE[Complete]
    RB --> STABLE[Stable Version]
